articles.title: Identification of siRNA silencing TGFβ1 and VEGFR2 and utility of the combination in targeting immune modulation and angiogenesis in treating melanoma in vivo.
articles.summary: Targeted siRNA therapy effectively silenced key melanoma-associated genes, reducing tumor growth, metastasis, and improving survival in experimental mouse models.

articles.title: Endobronchial ultrasound-guided mediastinal biopsies for the diagnosis of mediastinal diseases: A network meta-analysis.
articles.summary: A network meta-analysis shows endobronchial ultrasound-guided biopsies effectively diagnose mediastinal diseases, particularly in lung cancer staging.
